{"tid":1669423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[煲大佢] 資助120蚊買機票=公帑起三跑","createTime":"2019-10-22T14:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T16:01:57.000Z","uid":95138,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5a003ef3517c7c4a6987a12e793bdff8845ab863","tid":1669423,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"當年政府避開立法會財委會 <br />\n由機管局喺每張機票收三跑建設稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家每張機票都包含90至180蚊不等嘅三跑建設稅<br />\n<br />\n哩排機場生意慘淡 AA收少左好多三跑稅<br />\n依家波叔資助$120買機票 就等於用送錢俾AA、用公帑起三跑<br />\n<br />\n當年政府千方百計避開立法會<br />\n唔可以咁易俾佢得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59yXNSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59yXNSg.jpg&h=903b1dc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"000ee9178a2d0012703d9f336022e2cc94f398af","tid":1669423,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"120蚊=送錢俾AA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387ae29c9bcde0de3b5db0820f02c7f670d550b5","tid":1669423,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"三跑條數收唔夠錢就諗條咁嘅屎橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41ee46f244a1cac6d60548aab24ab09ae70d180","tid":1669423,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"唔係炒咗車咩"},{"pid":"d75eadff5b1b503ace3f2b404939adb521d72248","tid":1669423,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"短途機=公帑俾100%三跑稅"},{"pid":"2fe59c2d137423cc0d98bd1a5650ae27c9ed342c","tid":1669423,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f41ee46f244a1cac6d60548aab24ab09ae70d180","tid":1669423,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"